N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 450.13 - Continuation of existing proceedings

State Regulations

Every act or deed done or performed pursuant to the
provisions of the rules repealed shall remain and continue to be valid under
the provisions of this Part. Notes
